body:
Comic Book Review: The Black Order #1

I did not read Infinity War, but I would be damned if I didn’t read a limited series involving The Black Order. If you know me, then you know that sometimes I have a soft spot for villain stories. Not in the sense that I am one of those who likes to sympathize with them, because that’s not the point in being a villain. I have a soft spot for them because sometimes you need that book or two where…
